ComicInfo.Summary: After healing and extensive re-training, we follow the Objective Five team to China. They are sent to investigate, evaluate, and cause havoc in the red Republic. Disregarding an international moratorium on Biological Weapons, the Chinese have picked up where the Soviets left off. Lark, Alexis and DJ are given another chance to prove themselves by dropping a DNA-enhanced-super-soldier-monkey-wrench into their works.
